{NORTH indicates an above normal opening with five ♠s by her 3NT rebid.

SOUTH also has some extra strength so he makes a Control showing bid of 4

♥

.

Despite both partners showing extra strength North merely signs of at 4♠. Why? Because SOUTH's

Control bid of 4

♥

denied first-round control in both ♣s and

♦

s. NORTH realized she was off two Aces.}
